name: Hiccup
bio: Hiccup is a good boy and really loves to run!

name: Mocha
bio: Mocha is a good girl, she likes to run and will get away so we need to play in a place that has a fence!

name: Kipo
bio: Kipo has a brother named Scooby they are great together but are always down to play with others

name: Scooby
bio: Scoody is a good boy. He has a new sister Kipo that is keeping him busy but he is always down to play with others!

name: The Italian
bio: Italy is a good girl and she loves to roll around with other dogs. She is small and like to play hard so I want her to play with other small rambunctious dogs!

name: Hicarue
bio: A very playful guy that can play hard but also be very gentle

name: Buddy
bio: Loves to be outside all the time. Rain, Sun, Snow; doesn't matter.

name: Bubbu-ka-chue
bio: Gentle guy. Can really play with anyone at their level.

name: Thor
bio: Thor is a giant observer! He likes to play sometimes but also just mainly likes to watch the show.

name: Jello
bio: Always on the go looking for friends to go places with. Love going out and being on the go.

name: Jables
bio: Seeking all water dogs. Splashing, running in and out, shaking on the humans you name it if it's a water activity Jables is your doggy pal!

name: Rocket
bio: Very mellow will chase ball but really likes to just sniff and hang.

name: Pepi
bio: More energy then Pepi knows what to do with
